with three small projects,

36
00:01:38.040 --> 00:01:40.020
four medium size projects,

37
00:01:40.020 --> 00:01:42.040
and one large effort.

38
00:01:42.040 --> 00:01:45.000
Conversely, finance has both

39
00:01:45.000 --> 00:01:48.050
a few large projects and a few small or medium projects.

40
00:01:48.050 --> 00:01:51.070
What this tells me is that I'm going to need

41
00:01:51.070 --> 00:01:54.010
a different engagement strategy for finance

42
00:01:54.010 --> 00:01:57.090
