00:02:03.030 --> 00:02:04.090
When that's the case,

46
00:02:04.090 --> 00:02:08.040
communications about changes I'm making to processes

47
00:02:08.040 --> 00:02:13.010
will need to repeat over a longer period of time.

48
00:02:13.010 --> 00:02:15.010
When there are infrequent touch points,

49
00:02:15.010 --> 00:02:17.040
I'll have to repeat the information

50
00:02:17.040 --> 00:02:19.070
for a longer period before the changes

51
00:02:19.070 --> 00:02:21.070
become habit to them.

