00:02:21.070 --> 00:02:25.010
On the other hand, with claims and customer service,

53
00:02:25.010 --> 00:02:27.040
they interact with IT more often,

54
00:02:27.040 --> 00:02:32.000
so the changes will become normal for them fairly quickly.

